name: freezegun
raw_recipe:
package:
    name: freezegun
    version: 0.3.6

source:
    fn: freezegun-0.3.6.tar.gz
    url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/f/freezegun/freezegun-0.3.6.tar.gz
    md5: c321cf7392343f91e524eec0b601e8ec

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
        - six
        - python-dateutil >=1.0,!=2.0
    run:
        - python
        - six
        - python-dateutil >=1.0,!=2.0

test:
    imports:
        - freezegun

about:
    home: https://github.com/spulec/freezegun
    license: Apache-2.0
    summary: Let your Python tests travel through time

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf

about.summary: Let your Python tests travel through time
